/** specs
            +-STOP--ALLEOF----+ (3)  v-----------------------------------------+
 >>--SPECs--+-----------------+------+--+-| Group |--------------------------+-+---------><
            +-STOP-+-ANYEOF-+-+ (3)     +-READ-------------------------------+
                   +-n------+   (3)     +-READSTOP---------------------------+ (3)
                                        +-WRITE------------------------------+
                                        +-SELECT-+-streamnum-+---------------+
                                        |        +-streamid--+               |
                                        +-PAD--+-char----+-------------------+
                                        |      +-hexchar-+                   |
                                        |      +-BLANK---+                   |
